title: About
text:

title: Home
text:
This is my website. My project is about speed cubers and where they come from.


















The fastest solver is Yusheng Du. He is from China but the most solvers in the top 10 are from the USA.

title: Sources
text:
I used data from Kaggle called “Top 1000 Fastest Rubik’s Cube Solves”. The dataset was created 2023.
You can see that site in this link.
https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/darshanvss/top-1000-fastest-rubiks-cube-solves
